name: secret
description:
Imagine she has a secret

She is carrying it with her, close to her heart as she is guided by aliens in the dark - it was her destiny - to ensure a triumph, to ensure there is a new day. To ensure that there is a continuation of her beautiful story, the story of all heroines and heros, of goddesses and gods, of artists and collectors, of aliens and people, of all those without or with ai.
